@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@accessToken = REPLACE_WITH_ACCESS_TOKEN
@childId = child_1
@measurementId = measurement_1

### 정식 측정 생성 및 진단
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/children/{{childId}}/measurements
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "OFFICIAL",
  "measuredAt": "2026-07-19",
  "items": [
    { "itemKey": "CARDIO", "value": 63 },
    { "itemKey": "GRIP", "value": 53.8 },
    { "itemKey": "MUSCULAR_END", "value": 9 },
    { "itemKey": "FLEXIBILITY", "value": 12 },
    { "itemKey": "AGILITY", "value": 9.46 },
    { "itemKey": "POWER", "value": 105 },
    { "itemKey": "COORDINATION", "value": 23.21 }
  ]
}

### 자가 측정 생성
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/children/{{childId}}/measurements
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "type": "SELF",
  "measuredAt": "2026-07-20",
  "items": [
    { "itemKey": "CARDIO", "value": 40 },
    { "itemKey": "GRIP", "value": 42 },
    { "itemKey": "MUSCULAR_END", "value": 3 },
    { "itemKey": "FLEXIBILITY", "value": 8 },
    { "itemKey": "BMI", "value": 18.5 }
  ]
}

### 측정 목록
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/children/{{childId}}/measurements?type=OFFICIAL&page=1&size=20&sort=measuredAt,desc
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 측정 상세
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/measurements/{{measurementId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 성장 추적 - 특정 항목
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/children/{{childId}}/growth?itemKey=CARDIO
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 성장 추적 - 전체 항목
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/children/{{childId}}/growth
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 측정 삭제
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/v1/measurements/{{measurementId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
